Package Application.Utils

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AchievementUtils
    Utility class used to create new Achievements.
    CodeManagement
    Utility class used to check and update the access code of a User.
    See User.accessCode.
    CookieManagement
    Utility class used to create new User cookie identifiers.
    DumpData
    Utility class used to create and download data related to a Scenario.
    ImageFinder
    Utility class used to find images that may have already been loaded.
    ImageProcessor
    Utility class used to create the photo collage of a given Vision.
    Information about the size are pulled from the application's property file.
    LanguageFilesUtils
    Utility class used to access language files when the application is deployed and running jar.
    PaletteManagement
    Utility class used to manage the colors assigned to each emotion and to manage the combination of Feeling.
    This is reflected in a User profile page.
    ReadPropertyFiles
    Utility class used to read the property file of the application.
    TranslationUtil
    Utility class used to translate terms for the photo collage of a new Vision.
    UnsplashConnector
    Utility class used to query and return results from Unsplash for creating new Visions.
